      • ordering

        public abstract java.lang.String ordering
        Override for "natural order" of command within plugin May be either numeric (@see Integer.decode(String)) or string. If numeric, ordering will be upon numeric value, otherwise alphanumeric ordering will be undertaken. If not specified, user displayable name of command (calculated value) will be used for "natural ordering" of commands.
        Default:
        ""
